{"tid":1200092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發！］老燒話依家應該全體非建制議員總辭、絕食！！","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:17:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32ebdbdf44345d85cc16ae4426c9ec8536b5945e","tid":1200092,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xgb2Ov2LhFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxgb2Ov2LhFE&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=e47a6c26\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xgb2Ov2LhFE</a><br />\n<br />\n9:30<br />\n<br />\n前面老憑有啲話唔好暴力、繼續和理非<br />\n但其他都值得聽<br />\n（公道講部分係執番郁民口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"819dadd640f07edfb3db3f3fd8d65be45465981e","tid":1200092,"uid":105691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"屌你 又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a968279b298e31b84b195bd1c5a2cfba5b6b6fd","tid":1200092,"uid":171192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"小心販民班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日聲稱預演點知叫人散水<br />\n今日聲稱好嬲又咩都唔做<br />\n消耗士氣力量高手<br />\n推到販民仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c60f942d9ce95b72b3fc1faec4184b73d76b53","tid":1200092,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"聲援香港遊行　羅哲斯：絕食 36 小時　抗議港府無視反送中遊行<br />\n<br />\n立場報道2019/6/10 &mdash; 11:06<br />\n政府未有理會逾百萬人上街，堅持在周三立法會大會恢復逃犯條例修例二讀，「香港觀察」主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）在其社交媒體撰文，指自己會在今日早上開始為期36小時的絕食行動，以抗議政府無視昨日的反送中遊行，在立法會恢復《逃犯條例草案》二讀辯論，並希望政府能撤回決定。<br />\n<br />\n他指中國沒有獨立的司法制度，與香港迴異，表示修訂《條例草案》會破壞「一國兩制」。即使早前商界、法律界、人權組織及外國駐港商會對草案有所憂慮，政府仍無視民意，強行修訂逃犯條例，他對此感到不滿。 他表示因為要出席「香港觀察」的晚宴，會在星期二（六月十一日）晚暫緩絕食，但不排除會在日後恢復絕食，或採取更進一步的行動。<br />\n<br />\n羅哲斯是英國保守黨成員，曾公開評論香港人權、自由倒退，2017年被香港拒絶入境及遣返。當時英國外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）對事件表示「非常關切」，指英國當局已要求中國及香港政府交代事件，並指香港的高度自治、權利及自由應得到尊重。特首林鄭月娥當時回應事件時指，不能評論個案詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/聲援香港遊行-羅哲斯-絕食-36-小時-抗議港府無視反送中遊行/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%BE%85%E5%93%B2%E6%96%AF-%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F-36-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%2F&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=4c22cbc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%BE%85%E5%93%B2%E6%96%AF-%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F-36-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%2F&h=1baa0980\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/聲援香港遊行-羅哲斯-絕食-36-小時-抗議港府無視反送中遊行/</a>"},{"pid":"9880dfa76dd22849d4bc5e0ffc45c716434ed048","tid":1200092,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8018b79ed16ad47b4a7f817050e8d9a4a371bf51","tid":1200092,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a968279b298e31b84b195bd1c5a2cfba5b6b6fd","tid":1200092,"uid":171192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"小心販民班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日聲稱預演點知叫人散水<br />\n今日聲稱好嬲又咩都唔做<br />\n消耗士氣力量高手<br />\n推到販民仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hk